Day 72: Jenkins Parameterized Builds

Date: November 12, 2025
Overview
Made builds flexible with parameters.
Key Concepts Learned

String parameters
Choice parameters
Boolean parameters
Parameter usage in scripts

Configuration
groovyparameters {
    string(name: 'ENVIRONMENT', defaultValue: 'dev', description: 'Target environment')
    choice(name: 'BRANCH', choices: ['main', 'develop', 'staging'], description: 'Git branch')
    booleanParam(name: 'RUN_TESTS', defaultValue: true, description: 'Run tests?')
}

Challenges Faced
Validating parameter inputs and handling edge cases in build scripts.
